markdown#  Racing Game — Unity

An arcade reaction-based racing game. Reach the finish line before time runs out,
dodge bots and earn points for risky maneuvers.

## Gameplay

- **Controls** — WASD / Arrow keys, Space — handbrake (drift)
- **Q** — switch camera (follow / top view)
- Drive as close to bots as possible → earn **+500** bonus for each near miss
- Reach the finish line before the timer runs out → Win
- Crash or run out of time → Game Over

##  Progression

| Level | Time | Bots |
|-------|------|------|
| 1 | 30 sec | slow |
| 2 | 27 sec | faster, change lanes more often |
| 3+ | less | even more aggressive |

## Built With

- **Unity** (C#)
- Custom suspension physics (Raycast / SphereCast)
- Drift system
- Procedural bot spawning

##  Scripts
GameManager.cs       — game state, timer, score, levels
BotCar.cs            — bot behaviour
BotSpawner.cs        — bot spawning and despawning
NearMissDetector.cs  — near miss bonus
CollisionDetector.cs — collision → Game Over
FinishLine.cs        — finish line → Win
GameUI.cs            — all UI
CameraSwitcher.cs    — camera switch (Q)
CarController.cs     — player car physics

## Getting Started

1. Clone the repository
2. Open in Unity (2022+)
3. Open scene `Assets/Scenes/Main`
4. Press Play
